<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Farmhouse Frames</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            background-color: #faf8f5;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #e8dfd3;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #d4c7b8;
            padding: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 25px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #7a5c3a;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h2 {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #d4c7b8;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #7a5c3a;
        }
        .product-list, .collection-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #e8dfd3;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>Farmhouse Frames</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#collections">Collections</a>
    <a href="#products">Products</a>
    <a href="#fulfillment">Pickup & Shipping</a>
    <a href="#certificates">Certificates</a>
</nav>

<section class="section" id="home">
    <h2>Welcome to Farmhouse Frames</h2>
    <p>Authentic Kentucky photography transformed into premium wall art, puzzles, and home décor. Every piece is captured locally, enhanced professionally, and handcrafted into a product you’ll be proud to display.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="collections">
    <h2>Collections</h2>
    <div class="collection-list">
        <div class="card">Southern Springs & Still Waters</div>
        <div class="card">Woodland Falls</div>
        <div class="card">Winter Roads & Rural Frost</div>
        <div class="card">Forgotten Structures</div>
        <div class="card">Woodland Giants</div>
        <div class="card">Lakeside Horizons</div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="products">
    <h2>Products</h2>

    <h3>Premium Gallery-Wrapped Canvas</h3>
    <div class="product-list">
        <div class="card">8×10 — $49</div>
        <div class="card">12×16 — $69</div>
        <div class="card">12×18 — $72</div>
        <div class="card">16×24 — $90</div>
        <div class="card">12×36 — $105</div>
        <div class="card">24×36 — $132</div>
        <div class="card">20×60 — $159</div>
    </div>

    <h3>Puzzles</h3>
    <div class="product-list">
        <div class="card">8×10 Puzzle — 110 Pieces</div>
        <div class="card">11×14 Puzzle — 252 Pieces</div>
    </div>

    <h3>Mounted Prints</h3>
    <p>Available in multiple sizes. Same-day Walmart fulfillment.</p>

    <h3>Desk Canvas</h3>
    <p>5×7 and 8×10 same-day options.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="fulfillment">
    <h2>Pickup & Shipping</h2>
    <p><strong>Pickup Locations:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Cadiz — Monday & Wednesday (2–3 PM)</li>
        <li>Hopkinsville — Tuesday & Thursday (2–3 PM)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Multiple customers may be present during the same pickup window.</p>

    <p><strong>Shipping:</strong> Available for all products. Tracking provided once shipped.</p>

    <p><strong>Delivery:</strong> Not offered.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="certificates">
    <h2>Certificates of Authenticity</h2>
    <p>Every premium canvas and mounted print includes a certificate with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Artwork title</li>
        <li>Location</li>
        <li>Collection</li>
        <li>Date captured</li>
        <li>Product type</li>
        <li>Artist signature</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 Farmhouse Frames — Authentic Kentucky Photography
</footer>

</body>
</html>
